  <brief_title>A Study to Test the Effectiveness and Safety of a New Medication in the Treatment of Schizophrenia</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-blind Fixed-dose Study of Lurasidone (SM-13496) and Placebo in the Treatment of Schizophrenia</official_title>
